            "title": "盤中速報 - 順德(2351)股價殺至跌停，跌停價149.5元，成交26,377張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>順德(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2351:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2351\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2351-TW</a>)23日12:07下跌16.5元，股價跌停報149.5元，委賣2,792張，成交26,377張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為半導體導線架。五金文具用品。模具及其他。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>順德(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2351:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2351\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2351-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲37.19%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.15%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-4,924 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-4,952 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+142 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-114 張</li> <li>融資增減：+6,918 張</li> <li>融券增減：+957 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
