            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>仲琦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2419:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2419\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2419-TW</a>)23日12:02下跌3.5元，股價跌停報31.7元，委賣97張，成交9,033張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為通訊、電信產品。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>仲琦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2419:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2419\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2419-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲0.57%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.15%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,614 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,401 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+169 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+44 張</li> <li>融資增減：+52 張</li> <li>融券增減：-3 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
